{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/zhi-wu-qiang-zao-jing-rang-ni-de-dian-pu-geng-ju-te-se/","webpackCompilationHash":"c05de8f8e24aa66aa83f","result":{"data":{"ghostPost":{"id":"Ghost__Post__5d11d3f895f47f36568541fc","title":"植物墙造景，让你的店铺更具特色！","slug":"zhi-wu-qiang-zao-jing-rang-ni-de-dian-pu-geng-ju-te-se","featured":false,"feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/9-1-1.jpg","excerpt":"对于很多商店来说，现在市场竞争越来越激烈。单一化的装修格调，很难使客户有独特的消费体验。","custom_excerpt":"对于很多商店来说，现在市场竞争越来越激烈。单一化的装修格调，很难使客户有独特的消费体验。","created_at_pretty":"25 June, 2019","published_at_pretty":"25 June, 2019","updated_at_pretty":"26 June, 2019","created_at":"2019-06-25T15:57:44.000+08:00","published_at":"2019-06-25T16:00:42.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-06-26T09:27:40.000+08:00","meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"og_description":null,"og_image":null,"og_title":null,"twitter_description":null,"twitter_image":null,"twitter_title":null,"authors":[{"name":"Jason","slug":"jason","bio":null,"profile_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/icons8-customer-100.png","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":"https://new.a-green.cn"}],"primary_author":{"name":"Jason","slug":"jason","bio":null,"profile_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/icons8-customer-100.png","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":"https://new.a-green.cn"},"primary_tag":{"name":"墙面绿化","slug":"qiang-mian-lu-hua","description":"室内墙面绿化、室外墙面绿化","feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/2-1.jpeg","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},"tags":[{"name":"墙面绿化","slug":"qiang-mian-lu-hua","description":"室内墙面绿化、室外墙面绿化","feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/2-1.jpeg","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},{"name":"#室内墙面绿化","slug":"hash-shi-nei-qiang-mian-lu-hua","description":null,"feature_image":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520157646479-22f25713523d?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&q=80&fm=jpg&crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&w=1080&fit=max&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjExNzczfQ","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"internal"}],"plaintext":"对于很多商店来说，现在市场竞争越来越激烈。单一化的装修格调，很难使客户有独特的消费体验。而消费的减少会直接影响其盈利水平，这使的很多商店在经营上越发困难！\n\n国外很多商店为避免这种情况，会在室内打造生机勃勃的植物墙。这种室内造景的方式，可增加室内景观让客户有更加愉悦的购物体验。同时在与对手竞争时，植物墙能帮助品牌在客户的心理上建立印象认知。\n\n营业不佳有多方面因素，但富有特色的装修是吸引客户到店消费的一大利器。很多商店其环境一般、装修一般、视觉设计一般、整体给人感觉死气沉沉，这更别说让人前来消费。好的设计是通向成功的第一步！\n\n植物墙能增加室内生机，使购物过程不在枯燥无味。并且植物墙能够传达其健康的品牌理念，向客户表明其产品健康的自然性、无污染、无化学性。\n\n目前，越来越多的商家开始在自家的店铺内增加绿植。绿植能使整个店铺更具郁郁葱葱的生机和文化特色。在一些美食店，用植物墙做装饰点缀，不仅能体现其食材的自然性，也能展示其就餐环境的干净性。","html":"<p>对于很多商店来说，现在市场竞争越来越激烈。单一化的装修格调，很难使客户有独特的消费体验。而消费的减少会直接影响其盈利水平，这使的很多商店在经营上越发困难！</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/1-4.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/2-2.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>国外很多商店为避免这种情况，会在室内打造生机勃勃的植物墙。这种室内造景的方式，可增加室内景观让客户有更加愉悦的购物体验。同时在与对手竞争时，植物墙能帮助品牌在客户的心理上建立印象认知。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/3-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/4-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>营业不佳有多方面因素，但富有特色的装修是吸引客户到店消费的一大利器。很多商店其环境一般、装修一般、视觉设计一般、整体给人感觉死气沉沉，这更别说让人前来消费。好的设计是通向成功的第一步！</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/5-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/6-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>植物墙能增加室内生机，使购物过程不在枯燥无味。并且植物墙能够传达其健康的品牌理念，向客户表明其产品健康的自然性、无污染、无化学性。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/7.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/8.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>目前，越来越多的商家开始在自家的店铺内增加绿植。绿植能使整个店铺更具郁郁葱葱的生机和文化特色。在一些美食店，用植物墙做装饰点缀，不仅能体现其食材的自然性，也能展示其就餐环境的干净性。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/9-1.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/10.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image-->","url":"https://new.a-green.cn/zhi-wu-qiang-zao-jing-rang-ni-de-dian-pu-geng-ju-te-se/","uuid":"90f16ea3-7681-45f5-8267-1ab11fa0273c","page":false,"codeinjection_foot":null,"codeinjection_head":null,"codeinjection_styles":null,"comment_id":"5d11d3f895f47f36568541fc"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"zhi-wu-qiang-zao-jing-rang-ni-de-dian-pu-geng-ju-te-se"}}}